OL,5, The head of Scotland's drug deaths     
OL,6, taskforce has called for an overhaul of
OL,7, addiction services and reform of drugs 
OL,8, laws to halt overdose deaths.          
OL,10,FDavid Strang made the comments as the  
OL,11,FScottish government-established group  
OL,12,Fpublished its final report.            
OL,14,FIts "Changing Lives" report makes 20   
OL,15,Frecommendations and 139 action points  
OL,16,Fthat it says will help turn around     
OL,17,FScotland's record drug death numbers.  
OL,19,FIn 2020, 1,339 people died as a result 
OL,20,Fof a drug overdose.                    
